formulas.description: Criteria to send Tax Res email alert when status is updated to the research in progress.
formulas.name: varResearchEmailCriteria
formulas.expression: {!$Record.RecordType.Name} = 'Tax Res' && ISPICKVAL( {!$Record.Status} , 'Research in progress' ) && ISCHANGED({!$Record.Status}) && {!$Record.IsClosed} = false && ( ISBLANK( {!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c}) || ( NOT( INCLUDES({!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c} , 'Tax Res Research in progress Email' ) ) && NOT( INCLUDES({!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c} , 'P&I Late Deposit/Amendment Partial Auto-Solve Fired' ) ) ) ) && NOT( INCLUDES({!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c} , 'Skip Research in progress Email' ) ) && NOT( INCLUDES({!$Record.Action_Taken__c} , 'Skip Email Alert' ) )

formulas.name: varResearchEmailWhenPnIDeclines
formulas.expression: {!$Record.RecordType.Name} = 'Tax Res' && ISPICKVAL( {!$Record.Status} , 'Research in progress' ) && {!$Record.IsClosed} = false && ( ISBLANK( {!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c}) || NOT(INCLUDES({!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c} , 'Tax Res Research in progress Email')) && NOT( INCLUDES({!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c} , 'P&I Late Deposit/Amendment Partial Auto-Solve Fired') ) && INCLUDES({!$Record__Prior.Mass_Email_Step__c} , 'P&I Late Deposit/Amendment Partial Auto-Solve Fired') && NOT( INCLUDES({!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c} , 'P&I Late Deposit/Amendment Auto-Solve Fired') ) ) && NOT( INCLUDES({!$Record.Mass_Email_Step__c} , 'Skip Research in progress Email' ) ) && NOT( INCLUDES({!$Record.Action_Taken__c} , 'Skip Email Alert' ) )

textTemplates.name: tempChecklistEmail
textTemplates.text:
Thank you for your email and reaching out to Gusto. We know that receiving a tax notice can be a frustrating experience -- and here on the Tax Resolution team, were here to make sure we support you through this process.


Whats Next?

Your case will be assigned directly to a Tax Resolution Notice Specialist who will verify that we have the necessary information to begin the investigation. Once confirmed, well begin researching your notice and will communicate with the issuing Tax Agency on your behalf. If we need further clarification from you, the Specialist assigned to your case will contact you directly. At this point, there is no required action on your part. 


Once your case has been resolved, youll receive an email confirmation with details. 


Reminder: Gusto does not receive notices from any agenciesthey're only sent to the company directly. For more information on how to handle these notices in the future, head to this Help Center article. 


We appreciate the opportunity to partner with you in building & growing your business and look forward to supporting you through this Tax Notice experience. 


All the best,

Tax Resolution Team

textTemplates.name: tempFBEDResearchEmail
textTemplates.text:
As {!$Record.Account.Name}s payroll provider, Gusto recently received a tax notice directly from {!$Record.Agency_Information__r.Name} for your company. Were including a copy of this notice here for your information, but rest assuredtheres no action needed from you right now. 


Were assigning this case to a Tax Resolution Specialist whos skilled in handling this type of tax notice. If they determine we need more info from you to resolve this, well reach out to you via email.


Otherwise, once your case has been investigated and resolved, youll receive a confirmation email with details. 


If you have questions about this notice in the meantime, respond directly to this emailwe'll be happy to help you.


Sincerely,

The Gusto team

textTemplates.name: tempResearchEmail
textTemplates.text:
We've completed our initial review of your notice. Rest assured, your case is now in the hands of one of our dedicated Tax Resolution Specialists who specializes in handling cases like yours. Should our specialists require further information from you to proceed, they will contact you directly. Right now, there's no immediate action needed on your part.

Once your case is resolved, you'll receive a confirmation email with all the details.

If you've submitted multiple notices, each one will be carefully assigned to the most suitable Tax Specialist. You'll receive an email notification once a specialist is assigned to any additional notices.

Thank you for choosing Gusto as your partner in business growth. We're committed to serving you and look forward to resolving this matter efficiently.


Warm regards,

Gusto Tax Resolution Team
